  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Ages 18-75 years old that received at least one IT. Participants will be obtained from the
        pool of islet transplant recipients transplanted at the Diabetes Research Institute at the
        University of Miami, Miller School of Medicine.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        1. History of at least one islet alone transplant (ie islet transplant in the absence of
        any other organ transplant).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Inability to provide written informed consent.

          2. Mentally unstable and/or unable to comply with the procedures of the study protocol.

          3. History of any solid organ transplant.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
